    <div>
    <h1>Green Breakfast Smoothie</h1>
        <p>This healthy smoothie recipe is packed with protein, fiber, unsaturated fats, and essential vitamins and minerals.</p>
        <img src="../recipe-pictures/green-breakfast-smoothie.png" alt="green-breakfast-smoothie">
        <h3>Ingredients</h3>
            <p>Below is a list of required ingredients:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>1 cup almond milk (or more if needed to blend)</li>
                <li>1 tbsp chia seeds</li>
                <li>1 cup spinach (not packed down)</li>
                <li>2 bananas, frozen</li>
                <li>1 cup mango (fresh or frozen)</li>
            </ul>
        <h3>How to make!</h3>
            <p>Place all ingredients in a blender; process until smooth.</p>
    </div>